  "richContent": "<p>仓位 &amp; 收益率</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>【150】仓位变动 </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A：44.62% → 44.01% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>H：9.54% → 9.55% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A+H：54.16% → 53.56% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>股：56.78% → 56.18% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>债：11.11% → 11.10% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>现金：32.11% → 32.72%   </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>行业：20.07% → 19.51% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>医药：10.75% → 10.13% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>昨日卖出后，是【150】大建仓以来，&quot;现金仓位&quot; 新高（超过3/20）； &quot;A股仓位、A+H仓位、权益类仓位&quot; 新低（超过4/10）的日子</p>\n<p></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>【S】仓位变动： </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A：59.24% → 59.29% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>H：12.44% → 12.48% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A+H：71.68% → 71.77% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>股：75.16% → 75.28% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>债：9.47% → 9.45% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>现金：15.37% → 15.27% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>行业：31.76% → 30.91% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>医药：15.78% → 14.90% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>价值（红利）：11.68% → 12.68% </p>\n<p></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/08A75AC8-84C4-48AE-81C9-12D2BEF970D1.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/949E0E4A-9BBC-426C-9432-CCEDCE163E30.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/28C2EEEC-FA06-4D76-8018-19C658D934A9.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/32B57D4D-78C1-48D5-8958-8FDDD47C40E5.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/95711EC6-AF83-47F7-9884-F45E2E6AA2F6.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/3DC9CD9E-04B3-454D-85A2-9F8BC0DDE14A.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/F5F1B02A-9A61-4E14-9D0E-0E0CD1D36148.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/62263BE3-1777-455A-B40A-EF54B5215753.png\" />",
